data.description: This block home is in the heart of the lively downtown district of Saint Cloud. LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION... within a short distance of chique restaurants, botique retail stores, coffee shops, lake shore, night life, and lots of Public Parking. The property is currently being used as a single family residence but is zoned for professional us with an abundance of surrounding properties already converted for commercial use. Rear alley entrance with a separate, detached garage provides you endless possibilities. Act now and own your own building in Osceola's best kept secret which can be occupied as a residence while you develop your plans to use it as a commercial property. This fabulous property is also minutes from the turnpike, golf courses, 25-30 mins to Orlando International Airport or Lake Nona Medical City, and don't forget a day at the Melbourne Beach or the theme parks... a MUST SEE. All dimensions are estimated, buyers’ responsibility to verify
